price: 72. Ma idinkaa kuwa u soo saara geedaha, mise Annaga (Alle ah) weeye soo saarayaasha?
arabic: ءَأَنتُمۡ أَنشَأۡتُمۡ شَجَرَتَهَآ أَمۡ نَحۡنُ ٱلۡمُنشِـُٔونَ

version.title: Somali translation - Jacob
